# Architecture

- **Next.js** (App Router) deployed on **Vercel**.
- API routes in `app/api/` run as **serverless functions** on Vercel.

## Folder structure

- UI routes and layouts: `app/`
- Reusable UI: `components/`
- Serverless APIs: `app/api/<name>/route.ts`
- Shared non-UI logic: `lib/` (pure utilities; avoid React in generic helpers unless intentional)

Add new sections here as the system grows (data flow, auth, storage, external services).
